author: lgo
msg: Fix test issues introduced in r25486.
* subversion/tests/cmdline/svntest/actions.py
(set_prop): write the property value to a file and then set it.
* subversion/tests/cmdline/lock_tests.py
(enforce_lock): the test framework doesn't support setting a prop value '*',
use a workaround by writing the value to a file (uses the new set_prop
function). Add expected_err when setting property value '    '.
(lock_and_exebit1, lock_and_exebit2): Add expected_err when setting property
value '    '.
